Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}仮面にかくす素顔
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.93,0:02:29.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}はるかな過去の絶望
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}変更不可能な
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.85,0:02:36.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}痛みのすべてThree hundred years
