Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:23.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲伤已烟消云散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}为了不让这份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:38.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}没有泪水的明天过后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}会有温柔的未来等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只属于自己的答案
